column72: Local public health agency internal policy
column75: ACHD's project lead convened a workgroup of dietitians and interested staff to develop a robust and equitable healthy meeting policy. We completed the final draft of on 3/11 and are scheduled to present our draft to ACHD's Public Health Leadership Team on April 11th for feedback and final approval.
column84: Currently in our coalition are our dental partners KIND and Salud and our child care center ECPAC. We met with each organization individually to inform them of the partnership's goal to reduce consumption of sugar-sweetened and discuss pursuing sugar reduction policies, specifically the HDKM policy, in Commerce City. However, we have not convened all partners at one time. We are waiting to do more outreach and recruitment, especially amongst restaurant owners, in Commerce City before convening/mobilizing.
